        - Even simple tasks like "Preheat oven", "Boil water", or "Set aside" should be their own steps.
        - Aim for 5-15 steps for most recipes.


        Output JSON format:
        {
            "name": "Recipe Name",
            "description": "Short summary",
            "instructionMode": "steps",
            "ingredients": [{ "raw": "...", "name": "...", "amount": "...", "unit": "...", "existingId": "MATCHED_ID_OR_NULL" }],
            "steps": [{ "text": "Step 1..." }],
            "categories": ["Dinner"],
            "nutrition": {
                "calories": 450,
